<p> <ul> (a) No Assignment/No Insurance. This Buyer Refund Policy is not intended to constitute an offer to insure, does not constitute insurance or an insurance contract, does not take the place of insurance obtained or obtainable by the Buyer, and the Buyer has not paid any premium in respect of the Buyer Refund Policy. The benefits provided under this Buyer Refund Policy are not assignable or transferable by you. </ul> 
